<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - 找不到頁面</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    .not-found {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .not-found-icon {
      font-size: 5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .not-found h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .not-found p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .not-found a {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .not-found a:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="not-found">
    <div class="not-found-icon">😕</div>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>找不到您要訪問的頁面</p>
    <a href="/">返回首頁</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
